# Healthcare Management System - Complete Documentation

## Project Overview

A full-stack healthcare management system built with Flask (backend) and Tailwind CSS (frontend). This application allows healthcare providers to manage patients, schedule appointments, and maintain medical records efficiently.

### Features
- 👥 Patient Registration & Management
- 📅 Appointment Scheduling System
- 📋 Medical Records Management
- 📊 Dashboard with Statistics
- 🔄 RESTful API Architecture
- 📱 Responsive Tailwind CSS UI
- 🚀 Real-time Data Updates

